description:

PLEASE READ IMPORTANT LISTING INFORMATION BELOW PRIOR TO PURCHASING.  THERE ARE NO REFUNDS ON DIGITAL ITEMS.

Studio 874 Design‚Äôs digital downloads are the perfect way to grow your design base and offer your clients on trend, as well as beautiful and classic designs.  This rhinestone instant download template includes the following formats: SVG, EPS, DXF, PLT, PNG and PDF, ensuring it is compatible with a wide variety of cutting software and machines, including the Silhouette and Cricut software.

PLEASE SEE LISTING PHOTO FOR DESIGN SIZE, STONE COUNT, AND STONE SIZE INFORMATION.

WHAT YOU WILL RECEIVE

You will receive a zip file containing SVG, EPS, DXF, PLT, PNG AND PDF files.  Designs will be separated by color and stone size.  All files are delivered in "Zip" folders.  Please make certain you have the knowledge and ability to unzip or extract files from zipped folders.

PLEASE READ!!

ATTENTION Cricut/Brother Users:  Your software has limitations regarding numbers of objects, size, etc.  Please follow the directions below:
Directions for Cricut/Brother Users:
1.	Download the ‚ÄúCricut‚Äù folder and unzip/extract contents.
2.	Upload the files one at a time into your software.
3.	DO NOT DELETE THE BOX.
4.	Select the entire thing, including the box ‚Äì Make sure you are 	selecting both.  Resize to the measurements listed below the box.  PLEASE NOTE: You are only resizing the design and the box, NOT the measurements.
5.	Delete the measurements.
6.	Once you have resized, you can either keep or delete the boxes based on your preference ‚Äì I prefer to cut with the boxes.
7.	Cut
8.	Repeat for each ‚Äúlayer‚Äù included. 

ATTENTION Silhouette Cameo users:  In order to use the SVG files included, you will need to have the upgraded Silhouette software (Designer Edition or higher).  There is a DXF file included that will work with the basic software; however, please be certain that you know how to work with DXF files within the basic software prior to purchasing.  There is some manipulating that you will need to do.  

I strongly suggest that if you are not familiar with cutting rhinestone templates that you visit YouTube and search for how to videos.  

I do offer ready to press rhinestone transfers and/or pre-cut flock templates for most of my digital designs. If you are interested in a rhinestone transfer or flock template mailed to you, please convo me.

Check out the rest of my designs here:
www.etsy.com/shop/studio874designs.com

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DELIVERY

**PLEASE NOTE: This design will be delivered as an INSTANT DOWNLOAD FILE, which will be available in your Etsy account after you finalize your purchase. You will NOT receive a physical item in the mail.  

Once your purchase is confirmed, you will receive an email from ETSY.  Please note that the email will not come from me.  Sellers have no access or control over when the email is sent.  This is completely controlled by Etsy, as are the downloads. You can also access your files within your account under "Purchases and Reviews."  Please read listing carefully as there are NO REFUNDS on digital downloads.  All sales are final.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

DESIGN INFORMATION:

Design dimensions (size) and stone count and stone size are listed on the listing photo.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

IMPORTANT INFO

By purchasing this file you are aware that you must have the software and equipment needed to use the file, as well as the knowledge of how to use the software and equipment.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TERMS OF USE

You may use Studio 874 Designs digital files to:
- Create physical products for personal or business use
- Create physical product to sell

You MAY NOT use Studio 874 Designs digital files to:
- Share, sell, or distribute the digital file in part or in whole in any way
- Sell design as a template
- Make transfers to sell (design must be on a finished product)

If you have any questions, please convo me and I will be happy to assist you.  There are no refunds or returns.  Please ask all questions prior to purchase.  There are NO REFUNDS on digital downloads.

title: READY TO PRESS, Heat Transfer, Sublimation Design, Fourth of July  sublimation image ,Fourth of July
description:
>THIS LISTING IS FOR SUBLIMATION TRANSFER ONLY ‚Äì READ FULL DETAILS BEFORE ORDERING<<

Our transfers come ready to heat press and will not have water-markings. BRKreationsBoutique takes pride in using only the highest quality sublimation printer inks and paper. They have been tested and proven to provide the best quality prints onto sublimation materials when applied properly. This is a great alternative to using vinyl! No more weeding or buying vinyl! HEAT PRESS IS REQUIRED - CANNOT USE IRON.

üìåSublimation can be done on LIGHT colored fabric, containing at least 65% polyester. The higher the polyester count, the better!

üìå TO ORDER
‚Ä¢Choose Transfer Size
-Youth 7‚Äù - 8‚Äù
-Adult 8.5‚Äù - 11‚Äù

**ASK FOR BULK ORDER PRICES**

These measurements are an estimate and might vary slightly. This measurement will be for the widest part of the image. If you have any questions or want to order a custom size, or design, message us!

üìåDISCLAIMER
Please do your research on sublimation prior to ordering as we are not responsible for any pressing errors. If done correctly, you image will be bold and vibrant. If your image is faded or washes out, you did not follow instructions. Colors may vary slightly from monitor. This listing is for SUBLIMATION transfers only. (NOT SCREEN PRINTS)

üìåRETURNS/EXCHANGES
Due to the nature of the product, we do not allow returns or exchanges. If there is an issue with your order, please contact us within 5 days of receiving your order! It is your responsibility to look over prints before pressing.

üìåMost transfers ship SAME or NEXT day! We are not responsible for shipping delays.

Have question? Message us! We are happy to help.The initial print coming out of the printer and to you may be dull and looks faded.

It is important to note that this is perfectly fine and in fact shows us that we are on the right track. 

The reason for this dull or faded looking print coming out of your printer is that sublimation ink is only activated at 392 degrees Farenhieht , and when placed under sufficient pressure. In other words, the correct colour will only appear on the final sublimated product ‚Äì after you have completed the sublimation process carefully.

CHANGES/CUSTOMS
I am not able to make changes or edits to any designs. All designs are sold as-is and should remain that way. There should be no editing of the files to change colors, add or remove items, or change the text. Also, I am not able to do custom orders at this time.

If you have a wish list or are looking for something specific, please ask. I may have exactly what you are looking for.

All shipping fees include handling fees. If you would like to combine shipping costs for more than one item, I would be happy to do so if you convo me before purchase.

Purchasing my item means you have read, understood and will abide by my policies. Sorry, I do not accept trades.

A bit about reserving Items. I am more than happy to reserve an item for you. However, recently, I have had buyers request to reserve items, only to back out at the last moment. (This has happened with at least the last 10 people who have requested to reserve an item.) While I understand that things do come up and do happen and that money is tight, this is not fair to other buyers or to me. To save time as well as hassle, I have some new policies regarding reserves.

1. You must pay (through PayPal) 20% of the item's price. This 20% will be put towards the purchase. However, this 20% is non refundable. If you have questions about this please ask. If you do not wish to put down 20%, then I cannot reserve an item for you. No exceptions.
2. You MUST tell me when you plan to purchase the item you have reserved.
3. If you cannot purchase the item by the date you have selected, please let me know. 4. If you do not purchase the item by the date you have given me, I will contact you. If I do not hear back from you, I will open the listing up to other buyers.

If you purchase an item that has been reserved for another buyer, I will unfortunately have to cancel the transaction and refund your payment.

Lastly, on the subject of reserved items, I must please ask, if you really do not intend to purchase the item, please do not ask me to reserve it for you. My time, as well as your time, is precious.

Thank you very much for your cooperation and your understanding.

Thanks for popping in. <3

title: Queen Consort Crown Jewels holographic metallic vegan handmade watercolor pink holo calligraphy ink hand lettering quarter pan or half pan
description:
Queen Consort, from Reneeissance Colours‚Äô Crown Jewels collection of vegan handmade watercolour paint, is a super sparkly pink holographic watercolor. It is inspired by the Queen Consort‚Äôs ring, whose ruby appears pink in photographs. It will show up on both white and black paper, but will require thicker application to appear opaque on white paper. 

To best capture the holographic sparkle in a photo or video, use your camera‚Äôs flash. All photos and videos in this listing were shot with an iPhone flash, unless stated otherwise.

The Crown Jewels Collection contains a mixture of colourshift, chrome, and holographic watercolours that reflect the dazzling beauty of the Crown Jewels, the alluring symbols of Britain‚Äôs monarchy housed at the Tower of London.

Every paint is handmade with love, which means you may notice some air bubbles, bumps, or cracks. This is completely normal and does not affect the quality of the paint. Every quarter pan is filled 3 times and every half pan is filled 4 times to ensure you get the most paint possible, though air bubbles do occasionally occur.

Our homemade binder is made with the highest quality gum arabic available. We do not use honey or any other animal products in our paints, so they are vegan-friendly.

Not intended for use on skin. Please do not ingest.

For best results, apply 1 to 2 drops of water to the paint and wait a minute, then reactivate the paint with a paint brush.

NOTE REGARDING MAGNETS: All paint pans will come with a magnet glued to the bottom. If you do not want a magnet, please let me know in the "Add a note to ReneeissanceColours" section during checkout. 

INTERNATIONAL SHIPPING NOTE: I am currently shipping from London, England. I offer affordable international shipping because I want to share my paint with everyone. However, the postal system has been slow and unpredictable lately, so your paints may take longer than usual to reach you. Once I post them, I have no control over how long they take to arrive. International standard shipping does not come with a tracking number. If you would like tracking, please choose the upgraded shipping option.

title: Calligraphy Housewarming Gift - Self Inking Return Address Stamp - Custom Return Label Stamp - Personalized Stamp Return Address
description:
Does your hand cramp up at the thought of writing your return address 100s of times?  Mine does!  These custom stamps will not only save you from the dreaded hand cramp, but they also add a beautiful touch to your envelopes!  I just love how a stamped return address looks on the back flap of an envelope.  

Now with more flexibility!  Choose from either a wood address stamp or a Trodat self-inking stamp, and pick your ink color as well.

If you're purchasing a wood stamp and you'd like more ink pad color options, additional colors and types of ink pads are available here: https://etsy.me/2MqDe5l

----------
TIMING
----------

I pride myself in providing quick and efficient service, and most customers have their stamps in hand within 5-7 business days after ordering (excludes Sat and Sun). Once I receive your order, you will receive a mock-up within 1-2 business days. After the mockup is approved for production, it takes 1-2 days for the stamp to ship. After that, it's up the post office to deliver to you in a timely manner.

At checkout, you can choose either first-class shipping, which typically takes 5-7 business days (although is sometimes faster!), or you can upgrade to priority mail which takes 2-3 business days depending on your location.  However, these delivery times are not guaranteed by the post office.Does your hand cramp up at the thought of writing your return address 100s of times?  Mine does!  These custom stamps will not only save you from the dreaded hand cramp, but they also add a beautiful touch to your envelopes!  I just love how a stamped return address looks on the back flap of an envelope.  

Now with more flexibility!  Choose from either a wood address stamp or a Trodat self-inking stamp, and pick your ink color as well.

If you're purchasing a wood stamp and you'd like more ink pad color options, additional colors and types of ink pads are available here: https://etsy.me/2MqDe5l

------------
DETAILS
------------

First, choose either a wood stamp or a self-inking stamp.  I personally love the wood stamps, because you can change ink colors at will!  Wood stamps arrive with handle installed.  You can also choose to add on a standard felt ink pad in blue, red, or black!

The self-inking stamps are the highly respected Trodat brand.  Choose from a variety of colorful inks, which will last for up to 10,000 impressions!  Note that you cannot easily change ink colors with self-inking stamps.

Next, enter the desired name and address exactly as you'd like it to appear on the stamp. I will contact you within 1-3 business days with a digital proof of your design.

Once you approve your proof, the stamp will be delivered to you in about 5-7 business days!

This stamp is roughly 1"x2.5", depending on your exact text. Stamp previews shows an accurate size on a 5√ó7‚Ä≥ envelope.

------------------------
ABOUT MY SHOP
------------------------

The purpose of my shop, Fresh Cut Prints is to encourage, send joy, and show love to others through the written word and good old-fashioned snail mail.  As a society we've become so isolated from one another, but we can change that, one card at a time.  #intentionalloveproject

Please feel free to contact me with any questions, and visit me online at
